==Roadmap==

0.1:
Read/write TGA
Read DDS
Convert DXT1 to RGB565
Convert DXT1 to RGBA8888 (more accurate)
Convert RGB565 to RGB888

0.2:
Write DDS
Read/write VTF
Convert DXT2/3 to RGBA8888
Convert DXT4/5 to RGBA8888

0.3:
Convert RGB565 to DXT1

0.4:
Convert RGBA8888 to DXT1
Convert RGBA8888 to DXT2/3
Convert RGBA8888 to DXT4/5

0.5:
Other pixfmts

0.6:
Scaling/filters/generate mipmaps/thumbnails

0.7:
Read/write PVR container
Convert PVRTC to pixfmt (?)

0.8:
Convert pixfmt (?) to PVRTC

0.9:
Pathfinding for automatic conversion

1.0:
Tests

1.1:
Read/write Maxis Raster (and others)
Read/write Nintendo BTI, JPA, and others

1.2:
Rotation
Flips

2.0:
OpenGL GPU support for loading (converting?) textures

2.1:
OpenGL GPU support for transformations

Future or unknown timeframe:
OpenCL and/or threading support, other optimizations
HDR
Non-linear colorspace (sRGB)
Cubemap/spheremap/envmap generation
External library usage (libtxc_dxtn, NVidia utils, DevIL, …)
Other compression schemes (3Dc, ASTC, ETC, FXT1, S2TC, …)
Bunches of filters
Dithering
Paletted images
Normal map generation from bumpmap
DirectX support
Color transformations
GUI
